| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1744 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f8f8b4f6-7df4-51cd-bb97-bba54c1defdd"
